## 2. OPEN MATERIAL TRANSFER AGREEMENT (Biological Sequences)

All amino acid sequences, nucleotide sequences, protein designs, and
biological constructs in this repository are released under the OpenMTA.

### OpenMTA Terms:
- FREE for academic research
- FREE for commercial development
- NO reach-through rights on derivatives
- NO royalties required
- ATTRIBUTION required

Full text: https://biobricks.org/openmta/

