## 4. PATENT DEDICATION (Public Domain)

### DEDICATION

All patentable inventions, methods, compositions of matter, and
processes contained in this repository are hereby IRREVOCABLY
DEDICATED TO THE PUBLIC DOMAIN for patent purposes.

The author(s) expressly disclaim any and all patent rights that may
arise from this work and commit to never seeking patent protection
for any invention disclosed herein.

### PRIOR ART ESTABLISHMENT

This repository constitutes a defensive publication establishing
PRIOR ART under:

- 35 U.S.C. § 102 (United States)
- EPC Article 54 (European Patent Convention)
- PCT Article 33 (Patent Cooperation Treaty)

Any patent application covering subject matter disclosed in this
repository is invalid due to lack of novelty.

### NO PATENT ASSERTION

The author(s) covenant to never assert patent claims against any
person or entity practicing the inventions disclosed herein.

