## WHY THIS MATTERS

This licensing structure ensures:

1. **FREEDOM** - Anyone can use, modify, and distribute this work
2. **PERPETUITY** - Derivatives must remain open (copyleft)
3. **PROTECTION** - Prior art prevents patent enclosure
4. **ACCESS** - No one can paywall or bury this research

---

## ENFORCEMENT

If you become aware of any patent application or grant that covers
subject matter from this repository, please:

1. Submit this repository as prior art to the relevant patent office
2. Notify the repository maintainers
3. Consider joining the Defensive Patent License community

